Welcome to Baldwin Parks Live and Archived Media

City Council meeting audio files are arranged by date, with the most recent at the top of the list. Click Listen to Audio to hear the meeting with documents, or Agenda / Minutes to see just the documents. You can also search the archives by typing keywords into the Search box.

Windows Media Player is required to listen to the audio. This can be downloaded for free from the Microsoft website here.

The minimum system requirements for listening to the Archived audio are available here.
